 Q.   Only the halfway stage, I shouldn't ask this, but are you ready to win again?   
SÃREN KJELDSEN:   Don't know.   I mean, the three times that I've won out here, I didn't know if I was ready to win or not.   It just turned out that way, but I think that you have to stay humble about these things.   
You do your thing and do the best you can.   Nobody's going to tackle you.   Nobody's going to steal your ball, hopefully, so you just play your ball and on Sunday you add up and see how you've done.  
   
 Q.   Certainly on those three occasions you did win, there were plenty of signs in the weeks and months beforehand, that the game was good, a solidity week‑in and week‑out and that's where you're getting back to.   
